quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  19,41,Ndipo kumbukira nkhani ya Abrahamu imene ili m’Buku. Iye adali Mtumwi ndi munthu wangwiro
  19,42,"Pamene iye adawauza bambo wake kuti, “Oh Abambo! Kodi inu mungalambire bwanji chinthu chimene sichingathe kumva, kuona kapena kukuthandizani pa chilichonse?”"
  19,43,“Ohabambo! Choonadichavumbulutsidwa kwa ine chimene sichinakufikireni inu. Kotero nditsatireni ine kuti ndikutsogolereni ku njira yoyenera.”
  19,44,“oh abambo! Musamapembedze Satana. Ndithudi Satana adanyoza Ambuye wachisoni chosatha.”
  19,45,“oh abambo! Ine ndili kuopa kuti chilango cha Mulungu chidzadza pa inu ndipo mudzakhala bwenzi la Satana.”
  19,46,"Abambo ake adati, “Kodi ukudana ndi milungu yanga iwe Abrahamu? Ukapanda kusiya ndidzakuponya miyala ndipo unditalikire pa kanthawi kochepa.”"
  19,47,"Abrahamu adati, “Mtendere ukhale kwa inu. Ine ndidzapempha Ambuye wanga kuti akukhululukireni popeza, Mulungu, kwa ine, ndi wokoma mtima.”"
  19,48,“Ine ndikuchokerani ndi zimene mumapembedza kuonjezera pa Mulungu. Ine ndidzapempha kwa Ambuye wanga ndipo ndikhulupirira kuti popembedza Ambuye wanga ndisadzakhale watsoka
  19,49,"Ndipo pamene Abrahamu adasiya anthu ake ndi mafano amene iwo anali kupembedza kuonjezera pa Mulungu, tidamupatsa Isake ndi Yakobo. Aliyense wa iwo tidamupanga kukhala Mtumwi"
  19,50,Ndipo tidawapatsa onse mituka kuchokera m’chifundo chathu ndipo tidawapanga iwo kukhala otchulidwa mwaulemu